name: Po due for delivery
query:
select
    po.transaction_date Date,po.name Id, po.schedule_date Reqd_By_Date, po.status, po.supplier, poi.item_code,poi.qty,poi.received_qty,po.supplier_name, po.per_received,poi.project,sp.pch_notification_mail_id
from 
`tabPurchase Order` po,`tabSupplier` sp,`tabPurchase Order Item` poi 
where po.supplier_name=sp.name and sp.supplier_group not in ('Transport','Services') and po.status =%(Status)s and po.per_received=%(Percent)s and 
sp.supplier_name=%(supplier)s and po.name=poi.parent
